{"word":"Ahitub","slug":"ahitub","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Ahitub</b> <a href=\"#/H285\">H285</a> <br/> 1. High priest, father of Ahiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=14&verse=3'>1Sa 14:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=22&verse=9'>1Sa 22:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=22&verse=12'>1Sa 22:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=22&verse=20'>1Sa 22:20</a><br/> 2. Father of Zadok<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=8&verse=17'>2Sa 8:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=18&verse=16'>1Ch 18:16</a><br/> 3. Ruler of the house of God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=9&verse=11'>1Ch 9:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=11&verse=11'>Neh 11:11</a><br/> 4. The Ahitub mentioned in 1Chr 6:8; 6:11; 6:12, is probably identical with the last described above, or else he is confused with Azariah, 2Chr 31:10<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=8'>1Ch 6:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=12'>1Ch 6:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=31&verse=10'>2Ch 31:10</a>"}]}